name: Synchronous Times Ahead
description:
First Game Jam ever!

Definitely didn't over plan and stay up all night cutting unfinishable features trying to make something playable.  I couldn't get the executable to compile (because last-second curse ;) ), so I uploaded the python file.  Plus this way, you can run it on something other than windows.   

The game is played in standard rhythm game fashion, though the levels are randomly generated because I ran out of time to make actually planned levels.  

Programming and art by: J Steinkampf

Music and sound effects by: Chris Steinkampf
